=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=4tZsnAbfvz4Q7kNvgGtH-Dn&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AaocoNMNKYn7-WkbaeBB_Pk&oh=00_AYCsttWrv1KMzWNbZeEexFREgb29WhZVBM0lVGxFLnaYTg&oe=66DECF1D"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "TrailerThumbnail.png", "id": "509747380621677", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031591_509747383955010_7293900799620714682_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Kjx1lDdOZIgQ7kNvgG5xsL8&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AaocoNMNKYn7-WkbaeBB_Pk&oh=00_AYCRRmtEoyIKUXFg3BWdH2ukLRZ-mtuSJiHPrleGFSAyMw&oe=66DEDA3F"}, "display_name": "Detour Bus Demo", "keywords": [], "long_description": "ARRIVING SUMMER 2022\nTHIS DEMO INCLUDES THE FIRST LEVEL OF DETOUR BUS\n\nDetour Bus is a VR construction-comedy adventure, where you build ridiculous winding highways, to take the dysfunctional Flowers family on a road trip across Post-Infrastructure America. Nostalgia junkie Daddy Flowers aims to revive his family's bonds before the end of summer vacation, but stuck together in a restored microbus, workaholic Momma, communist-in-training Junior, and social-media-baby Goldie have a lot more to fight about than unite over. Meanwhile, the open road is under threat; you'll have to get in the construction groove to take on corrupt Senator Joseph McCarthief\u2019s attempts to turn all freeways into pay-to-drive tunnels and reclaim your right to transportation.\n\nAccessibility Considerations:\none-button controls\ncaptioning\ndyslexia friendly fonts\nartificial locomotion incl. snap turning, smooth moving\nheight calibration\none-controller mode\nno-reach 3DoF mode\nbuttons-only mode\nfull button remapping", "short_description": "Snap together inconvenient road pieces to build ridiculously convoluted highways, and guide the dysfunctional Flowers family on a psychedelic road trip across post-infrastructure America."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://latestageinteractive.com/privac